                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h3>Phase 3: Complete Integration</h3>
                            <p>Implement more advanced concepts and fully integrate sustainability:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Strategic efficiency investments</li>
                                <li>Green marketing framework</li>
                                <li>Cross-module sustainability references</li>
                            </ul>
